answers.body_markdown:
Add a white space at the end of each line so that the keyword on the next line is not clumped with it, e.g.:

    sb.append(&quot;SELECT D.* &quot;);

instead of 

    sb.append(&quot;SELECT D.*&quot;);

and also remove the trailing semicolon.

